@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam backgroundColor white

title Process State Transition Diagram

[*] --> init : SHProcessCreate\nreceived

init --> running : AsyncIO process task\ncreates OS process;\nstdin/stdout/stderr\ntasks started

running --> complete : process exits;\nSHProcessExit sent\nto Global Services;\noutput tasks cancelled

complete --> [*] : process deleted\nfrom Local Services

running --> running : SHFwdInput\n(stdin written)\nor SHFwdOutput\n(stdout/stderr forwarded\nto Launcher/Backend)

note right of running
  Three AsyncIO tasks active:
  • stdout monitoring → SHFwdOutput
  • stderr monitoring → SHFwdOutput
  • stdin writing ← SHFwdInput
end note

@enduml
